Disney's stage version of #TheLittleMermaid took pains to address most of the other criticisms (I expect the live-action version to do this too!) but the issues with the dubious contracts and missing mermaids are too central to the story and Ursula's villainy to be changed...

Been listening to the #RevisionistHistory attack on #Disney's #TheLittleMermaid, but ultimately I can't escape the feeling @screenjunkies did it better with their #HonestTrailer, which made many of the same points in just 5 minutes...

Things get better in the second half, with more substantial (and funnier) criticisms of #TheLittleMermaid (many of which fans such as myself agree with!), but it still feels a bit overhyped...

#RevisionistHistory
